  "body": "**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**\r\n\r\nIn our mainnet node, some gossip blocks are ignored\r\n<img width=\"1246\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2022-01-13 at 14 18 01\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/10568965/149283540-32126fb4-788b-4e4b-9152-9036195e9f2b.png\">\r\n\r\nThe log shows that it's all `BLOCK_ERROR_PARENT_UNKNOWN` unknown error\r\n\r\n**Describe the solution you'd like**\r\n\r\nGiven this example\r\n\r\n```\r\nJan-13 00:37:47.577 [NETWORK]         ^[[34mdebug^[[39m: gossip - beacon_attestation - ignore slot=2934187, subnet=23, index=23, code=ATTESTATION_ERROR_UNKNOWN_BEACON_BLOCK_ROOT, root=0x144b0458d9fecfe537b2df6f07abda4e1ba5f708dcadb1454d0f11cad2789469\r\n```\r\n\r\nright now we only search for block until the next block comes\r\n```\r\nJan-13 00:38:00.259 [NETWORK]         ^[[34mdebug^[[39m: Gossip block has error slot=2934188, root=0xa11e…3e12, code=BLOCK_ERROR_PARENT_UNKNOWN\r\nJan-13 00:38:00.527 [NETWORK]         ^[[34mdebug^[[39m: Req  sending request method=beacon_blocks_by_root, encoding=ssz_snappy, client=Prysm, peer=16...zQhddr, requestId=661829, requestBody=[\"0x144b0458d9fecfe537b2df6f07abda4e1ba5f708dcadb1454d0f11cad2789469\"]\r\nJan-13 00:38:00.527 [NETWORK]         ^[[34mdebug^[[39m: Req  request sent method=beacon_blocks_by_root, encoding=ssz_snappy, client=Prysm, peer=16...zQhddr, requestId=661829\r\n```\r\n\r\n+ we should be able to search for the block right after we receive unknown block root gossip attestations. \r\n+ consider downscoring peer if we can't fetch that block.\r\n+ this is related to #3560",
