    "body": "> need to prioritize this, this is the metric on v1.4.2 mainnet node\r\n> \r\n> <img alt=\"Screenshot 2023-03-14 at 09 15 06\" width=\"1285\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/10568965/224875285-71640b59-ade6-486c-9ca1-756d25ad66f3.png\">\r\n> \r\n> expect to see block no later than 0.5s after we receive an unknown block attestations\r\n\r\nthis is mainly due to the I/O lag issue, not because of gossipsub's performance. Triggering block search does not help much since it still suffers from I/O lag issue.\r\n\r\nMost of the time at every slot, there's a race between gossip block and rpc block, and gossip block comes first",
